{"tid":1733022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大遭港警圍困恐血腥攤牌　路透社記者承諾同學生留守","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:49:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":541,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"9e792b79820ab873a73a54f80c2749a98198c621","tid":1733022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"香港理工大學校園內連日警民衝突不斷，《路透社》首席記者龐佛里特（ James Pomfret ）於 17 日晚間 11 點左右，透過個人推特發文說道他與《路透社》的團隊留在理大校園內，並表示「不論發生什麼事，我們都會留下」對於理大的情勢，龐佛里特透露現場瀰漫一股不祥的預感，擔憂攤牌時，將會迎來流血衝突。他描述，在理大現場有數以百計的示威者，在警方的包圍下，仍堅強的留守校園。<br />\n<br />\n    Inside Poly U now with a Reuters team. We&rsquo;ll stay whatever happens. A sense of foreboding amid grave fears of a bloody showdown, hundreds of tenacious and desperate protesters trapped on all sides by police, some highly on edge #HK #HongKongProtests #StandWithHongKong<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; James Pomfret (@jamespomfret) 2019年11月17日<br />\n<br />\n警方於 13 日進攻香港多間大學，其中以中文大學、理工大學衝突最為激烈。昨（ 17 ）晚，香港警方包圍理工大學，並透過臉書發布聲明宣稱不排除以實彈射擊，警告理大內所有人於 10 點前撤離校園，否則一律逮捕。理大校長滕錦光則透過影片對校內人士喊話，承諾警方不會再對校園內示威師生使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n然而在滕錦光發表談話後，警方依然對示威學生發射催淚彈，並在 17 日晚間 11 點左右，於理大校園周邊傳出多名身著便服的學生，即使依照警方指示離開校園，仍馬上被逮捕。今日（ 18 ）受困的學生試圖離開理大校園，卻遭警方發射催淚彈驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n根據龐佛里特的描述，被警方包圍的理大校園內，包含他在內共有 4 名《路透社》記者，包括駐香港記者潘潔西（ Jessie Pang ）、曾於南北韓、阿富汗採訪的史密斯（ Josh Smith ）和札哈里拉（ Marius Zaharia ），並表示團隊將會陸續更新現場情勢。後龐佛里特與其團隊透過推特上傳多支影片。<br />\n<br />\n    Reuters have four text correspondents inside Hong Kong&rsquo;s besieged Poly U, as police tighten the security cordon and bar access to outsiders, pls follow our updates. We&rsquo;re staying put @joshjonsmith @MZaharia @JessiePang0125 #HK #HongKongProtests #StandwithHK<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; James Pomfret (@jamespomfret) 2019年11月17日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    A protesters shouted desperately form the rooftop at the police, &ldquo;Remember you got life in your hand. Why you need to push us to death?&rdquo; #antielab #hongkongprotests <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/3t37wIpncn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2F3t37wIpncn&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=3bc0bca3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/3t37wIpncn</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Jessie Pang (@JessiePang0125) 2019年11月18日<br />\n<br />\n史密斯於今（ 17 ）上午 8 時左右發文，表示被困在理大內的示威學生，正試圖逃離理工大學，然而警方不斷對他們施放催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n    Protesters are making a desperate attempt to escape from Hong Kong&rsquo;s polytechnic university, facing off with riot police. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/N2PMMJqiWg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FN2PMMJqiWg&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=8448526b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/N2PMMJqiWg</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Josh Smith (@joshjonsmith) 2019年11月18日<br />\n<br />\n    Many of the protesters trying to escape don&rsquo;t have the gas masks needed to handle what the police are throwing at them<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Josh Smith (@joshjonsmith) 2019年11月18日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20191118/3761222/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20191118%2F3761222%2F&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=d1cc9e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20191118/3761222/</a>"},{"pid":"7d3bcf0294d65379012ec5d9170893c40e3ccc28","tid":1733022,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e41a1f7d1cea87ae452dfd213928094335be3d","tid":1733022,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0abe7137362784fa28b4aea24c6e4409649ecd","tid":1733022,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d7c50ee1615797f32f7e4b317abeb71e349574","tid":1733022,"uid":4574,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"真係多謝記者<br />\n<br />\n唔係屠城都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280e6c0de8dacb64431276e850297ed80f2f8972","tid":1733022,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6d08168d5b70cedf83df192252f77ac1987538","tid":1733022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af43b156b381d367b7dec1ee9c73cfe23bb1be6","tid":1733022,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd496c0901e647bbf63d9d8a34fb06585eac258","tid":1733022,"uid":259963,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"#手足投稿 #手足建議 <br />\n而家所有人唔應該塞曬係尖沙咀紅磡。留一批和理非係到聲援，另一批就去狗屋狗宿火攻。咁就可以引到理大現場嘅狗車調走。其他地方都要開花，以免可以支援到！<br />\n當狗車調走後會有缺口，手足就容易d係個缺口到返出黎！<br />\n根本而家係防到出面入唔到去，入面又出唔到黎。大家對恃最辛苦係入面嘅手足呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFm tg group"},{"pid":"076a678833c2356bf445c022bcab8fe86b731295","tid":1733022,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9e792b79820ab873a73a54f80c2749a98198c621","tid":1733022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"香港理工大學校園內連日警民衝突不斷，《路透社》首席記者龐佛里特（ James Pomfret ）於 17 日晚間 11 點左右，透過個人推特發文說道他與《路透社》的團隊留在理大校園內，並表示「不論發生什麼事，我們都會留下」對於理大的情勢，龐佛里特透露現場瀰漫一股不祥的預感，擔憂攤牌時，將會迎來流血衝突。他描述，在理大現場有數以百計的示威者，在警方的包圍下，仍堅強的留守校園。<br />\n<