data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/</a>"},{"pid":"928e877dbcb48d6e274b5db9edd498472d87671b","tid":1733022,"uid":302668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36edb19f371d88e39ddb02944054e276fad5cecf","tid":1733022,"uid":51701,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"70e819b2ca3b8c8e2ed8c6c5a49b0a844df7534e","tid":1733022,"uid":71428,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"記者免死金牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"其他一早散晒啦<br />\n都係路透社最堅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"可能有做過中東戰地記者"},{"pid":"baccb74307aee0de22eab3cc9b6ca97bb6a291a9","tid":1733022,"uid":292416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36edb19f371d88e39ddb02944054e276fad5cecf","tid":1733022,"uid":51701,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"70e819b2ca3b8c8e2ed8c6c5a49b0a844df7534e","tid":1733022,"uid":71428,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"記者免死金牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"其他一早散晒啦<br />\n都係路透社最堅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"鬼佬先有免死金牌，郁親外國人隨時百國聯軍"},{"pid":"c8a03b7fbc547045abd63566991eb32481266a72","tid":1733022,"uid":207872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e792b79820ab873a73a54f80c2749a98198c621","tid":1733022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"香港理工大學校園內連日警民衝突不斷，《路透社》首席記者龐佛里特（ James Pomfret ）於 17 日晚間 11 點左右，透過個人推特發文說道他與《路透社》的團隊留在理大校園內，並表示「不論發生什麼事，我們都會留下」對於理大的情勢，龐佛里特透露現場瀰漫一股不祥的預感，擔憂攤牌時，將會迎來流血衝突。他描述，在理大現場有數以百計的示威者，在警方的包圍下，仍堅強的留守校園。<br />\n<br />\n    Inside Poly U now with a Reuters team. We&rsquo;ll stay whatever happens. A sense of foreboding amid grave fears of a bloody showdown, hundreds of tenacious and desperate protesters trapped on all sides by police, some highly on edge #HK #HongKongProtests #StandWithHongKong<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; James Pomfret (@jamespomfret) 2019年11月17日<br />\n<br />\n警方於 13 日進攻香港多間大學，其中以中文大學、理工大學衝突最為激烈。昨（ 17 ）晚，香港警方包圍理工大學，並透過臉書發布聲明宣稱不排除以實彈射擊，警告理大內所有人於 10 點前撤離校園，否則一律逮捕。理大校長滕錦光則透過影片對校內人士喊話，承諾警方不會再對校園內示威師生使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n然而在滕錦光發表談話後，警方依然對示威學生發射催淚彈，並在 17 日晚間 11 點左右，於理大校園周邊傳出多名身著便服的學生，即使依照警方指示離開校園，仍馬上被逮捕。今日（ 18 ）受困的學生試圖離開理大校園，卻遭警方發射催淚彈驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n根據龐佛里特的描述，被警方包圍的理大校園內，包含他在內共有 4 名《路透社》記者，包括駐香港記者潘潔西（ Jessie Pang ）、曾於南北韓、阿富汗採訪的史密斯（ Josh Smith ）和札哈里拉（ Marius Zaharia ），並表示團隊將會陸續更新現場情勢。後龐佛里特與其團隊透過推特上傳多支影片。<br />\n<br />\n    Reuters have four text correspondents inside Hong Kong&rsquo;s besieged Poly U, as police tighten the security cordon and bar access to outsiders, pls follow our updates. We&rsquo;re staying put @joshjonsmith @MZaharia @JessiePang0125 #HK #HongKongProtests #StandwithHK<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; James Pomfret (@jamespomfret) 2019年11月17日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    A protesters shouted desperately form the rooftop at the police, &ldquo;Remember you got life in your hand. Why you need to push us to death?&rdquo; #antielab #hongkongprotests <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/3t37wIpncn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2F3t37wIpncn&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=3bc0bca3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/3t37wIpncn</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Jessie Pang (@JessiePang0125) 2019年11月18日<br />\n<br />\n史密斯於今（ 17 ）上午 8 時左右發文，表示被困在理大內的示威學生，正試圖逃離理工大學，然而警方不斷對他們施放催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n    Protesters are making a desperate attempt to escape from Hong Kong&rsquo;s polytechnic university, facing off with riot police. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/N2PMMJqiWg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FN2PMMJqiWg&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=8448526b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/N2PMMJqiWg</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Josh Smith (@joshjonsmith) 2019年11月18日<br />\n<br />\n    Many of the protesters trying to escape don&rsquo;t have the gas masks needed to handle what the police are throwing at them<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Josh Smith (@joshjonsmith) 2019年11月18日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20191118/3761222/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20191118%2F3761222%2F&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=d1cc9e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20191118/3761222/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75cc467ec965862c26d2cf3d25b9eaf7c8c125a7","tid":1733022,"uid":207872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5d7c50ee1615797f32f7e4b317abeb71e349574","tid":1733022,"uid":4574,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"真係多謝記者<br />\n<br />\n唔係屠城都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"138c0c1512328ce5e54cfb875cb4a9709eb074bd","tid":1733022,"uid":269179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a9c4fce0b77f62f8f63479707d92365085dc988","tid":1733022,"uid":326897,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e5d7c50ee1615797f32f7e4b317abeb71e349574","tid":1733022,"uid":4574,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"真係多謝記者<br />\n<br />\n唔係屠城都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"知道又點，rthk 影埋手足俾人暴打，<br />\n你又做得啲乜呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx0bJgW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx0bJgW.gif&h=13abd075&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5dc5eb078a58d08169f646239576032df47e992","tid":1733022,"uid":17838,"like